{"tid":1838990,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[無自由］阿嬌老公係咪禁止佢玩社交媒體？？？","createTime":"2020-01-24T08:30:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T15:54:23.000Z","uid":56716,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1b80340e9b9b65cc5ede55136cd46a0fdc5e8bf2","tid":1838990,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T08:30:58.000Z","msg":"阿嬌對上一次update ig已經係9月份嘅事，睇返佢以往都更新得幾密，而家已經4個月無update，fb更加成9個月無影，記得佢之前講過老公禁止佢同阿sa+joey去旅行，會唔會連ig fb都唔俾佢玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EPXWdxR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEPXWdxR.png&h=0b35c702&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5UUxwiu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5UUxwiu.png&h=f32fba3d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ai0dfLa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAi0dfLa.png&h=71c98d48&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FFnCHqc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFFnCHqc.png&h=3628b995&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">提起好姊妹蔡卓妍與容祖兒到北海道旅行，獨欠阿嬌，她說：「我冇放飛機呀，完全唔關我事，而家有屋企，要顧住老公，有家室嘅人你哋明唔明。」在逼供之下，阿嬌暗示老公下「禁令」，問她是否將丈夫放在首位？她說：「係！大家明啦！老公重要，姊妹都好重要，做人好難。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190226/59305576\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190226%2F59305576&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX9MQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=edcf0a89\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190226%2F59305576&h=294647e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190226/59305576</a>"},{"pid":"b549165be39e38b165c426e896b08e7192e8a833","tid":1838990,"uid":242537,"like":0